drinking problem 
on the other hand anybody who doesnt have compassion or 
sympathy for a kid that was jailed for part of his life for a crime 
that never occurred well that person has a bigger problem than my 
client 
dotsons problems began in 1977 when cathleen crowell webb then 
a high school student claimed she had been sexually assaulted and 
identified dotson as her attacker she said in 1985 after she had 
moved to new hampshire that she was never attacked and had wrongly 
accused dotson 
but by then he had been convicted of the rape and sent to tough 
state prisons where he ended up serving six years based on mrs 
