widening labor unrest and increasingly aware it was unable to 
control the economy offered to negotiate with solidarity 
five months later the communist party completed a dramatic 
political aboutface and opened the way for restoring legal status 
to the independent movement it had spent eight years fighting 
walesa though watched in the west went virtually unmentioned in 
the official polish press except occasionally as a private person 
a former leader of a former union or a tool of foreign powers 
when necessary his face was edited out of group photos 
only in september did he enter newspaper pages and television 
screens he remained there during the roundtable talks with 
communist authorities that unleashed political and trade union 
reforms 
by june solidarity candidates were allowed to run for all 100 
