the public health services efforts to prevent the spread of 
aids would be hampered significantly 
all federal aviation administration personnel including flight 
controllers might be furloughed for three days a month 
the internal revenue service might lose 4700 employees and 
reduce taxpayerassistance phone calls by 10 million 
the defense department could be forced to slash manpower by 
160000 
