on columbus ohio has filed a 3 million libel suit against the 
paper denying the allegations 
a native of mansfield ohio brown is a graduate of denison 
university and the yale law school he served as a staff attorney 
for the federal trade commission and as a deputy state attorney 
general from 1978 to 1982 
