her onewoman campaign against the campanile as the skyscraper 
would be called has made the 49yearold mrs kraus a local 
celebrity and the bane of developers planning other skyscrapers in 
frankfurt a world financial center 
mrs kraus has the right under hesse state law to block the 
campanile because it would cut her home off from sunlight and the 
