outside of utah likewise most of the genealogical helpers 50000 
subscribers are not mormon and do not live in utah 
theres a vast amount of interest hall said a lot of 
people think its totally fascinating to learn about their 
ancestors it gives them a feeling of heritage for the 
professional the most important thing is to have the detective 
feeling 
its kind of like the thrill of the hunt 
