30 totaled 489 million pounds or 3207 pence per share compared 
with 404 million pounds or 2674 pence in the same period a year 
ago 
sales rose 23 percent to 10 billion pounds from 813 billion 
pounds 
bat does not release quarterly results it is not required to 
under british law 
the companys financial services segment turned in the best 
performance operating profit surged to 398 million pounds from 177 
million pounds 
