insurance group inc the los angelesbased insurance company the 
conglomerate acquired last year for 52 billion 
bat said its tobacco business performed well contributing 404 
million pounds to operating profit compared with 361 million pounds 
a year ago 
the companys tobacco brands include kent and kool it also owns 
the saks fifth avenue and marshall fields stores 
